text: The Island of Stroma also known as the Isle of Stroma or just Stroma is an uninhabited island just off the north coast of Scotland in Caithness in the Highland Council Area.https://data.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/doc/50kGazetteer/126260 Viewed on 10/09/2022 == References == Category:Islands of Scotland
